hadiths[27]{hadithnumber,text}:
2711,"jab Suhail-bin-Amr ne ( Hudaibiya mein kuffaare-Quraish ki taraf se muaahida suleh ( likhwaayaa to jo sharaait Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney Suhel ne rakhi thin, unmein ye shart bhi thin ke ham mein se koi bhi shakhs agar aap ke yahan ( faraar ho kar) chala jaey chahe wo aap ke Deen par hi kyon na ho to aapko usey hamarey hawale karna hoga. musalman ye shart pasand nahi kar rahe they aur is par unhein dukh hua tha. lekin Suhel ne us shart ke baghair suleh qabool na ki. aakhir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usi shart par suleh naamaa likhwaa liya. ittifaq se isi din abu-jandal (Raziallahu anhu) ko jo musalman ho kar aaya tha (muaahide ke tehet naa chahtey huey) unke walid Suhail-bin-Amr ke hawale kar diya gaya. isi tarah muddate-suleh mein jo mard bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein (Makka se bhag kar aayaa) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey unke hawale kar diya. chahe wo musalman hi kyon na raha ho. lekin chand eman wali auratein bhi hijrat karke aa gaee thin, Umme- Kulsoom-bint-Aqba-bin-abii-Mueet (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unmein shamil thin jo isi din (Makka se nikal kar) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai thin, wo jawan thin aur jab unke ghar waley aaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se unki waapsii ka mutalba kya, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein unke hawale nahi farmaya, balke aurton ke mutaalliq Allah Taala (sura Mumtahina mein) irshad farma chuka thaa إذا جاءكم المؤمنات مهاجرات فامتحنوهن الله أعلم بإيمانهن‏ wla هم يحلون لهنtak ''jab musalman auratein tumharey yahan hijrat karke pahunchein to pahley tum unka imtihaan ley lo, yun to unke eman ke mutaalliq jaanney wala Allah Taala hi hai. Allah Taala ke us irshad tak ke ''kuffaar w mushrekeen unke liye halal nahi hain.''"
2712,"jab Suhail-bin-Amr ne ( Hudaibiya mein kuffaare-Quraish ki taraf se muaahida suleh ( likhwaayaa to jo sharaait Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney Suhel ne rakhi thin, unmein ye shart bhi thin ke ham mein se koi bhi shakhs agar aap ke yahan ( faraar ho kar) chala jaey chahe wo aap ke Deen par hi kyon na ho to aapko usey hamarey hawale karna hoga. musalman ye shart pasand nahi kar rahe they aur is par unhein dukh hua tha. lekin Suhel ne us shart ke baghair suleh qabool na ki. aakhir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usi shart par suleh naamaa likhwaa liya. ittifaq se isi din abu-jandal (Raziallahu anhu) ko jo musalman ho kar aaya tha (muaahide ke tehet naa chahtey huey) unke walid Suhail-bin-Amr ke hawale kar diya gaya. isi tarah muddate-suleh mein jo mard bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein (Makka se bhag kar aayaa) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey unke hawale kar diya. chahe wo musalman hi kyon na raha ho. lekin chand eman wali auratein bhi hijrat karke aa gaee thin, Umme- Kulsoom-bint-Aqba-bin-abii-Mueet (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unmein shamil thin jo isi din (Makka se nikal kar) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai thin, wo jawan thin aur jab unke ghar waley aaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se unki waapsii ka mutalba kya, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein unke hawale nahi farmaya, balke aurton ke mutaalliq Allah Taala (sura Mumtahina mein) irshad farma chuka thaa إذا جاءكم المؤمنات مهاجرات فامتحنوهن الله أعلم بإيمانهن‏ wla هم يحلون لهنtak ''jab musalman auratein tumharey yahan hijrat karke pahunchein to pahley tum unka imtihaan ley lo, yun to unke eman ke mutaalliq jaanney wala Allah Taala hi hai. Allah Taala ke us irshad tak ke ''kuffaar w mushrekeen unke liye halal nahi hain.''"
2713,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hijrat karne wali aurton ka us aayat ki wjah se imtihaan liya kartey they أيها الذين آمنوا إذا جاءكم المؤمنات مهاجرات فامتحنوهن Mina ( Mina إلى Mina ( Mina ghafoor رحيم‏ ''aey musalmaanon! jab tumharey yahan musalman auratein hijrat karke aaein to tum unka imtihaan ley lo غفور رحيم‏ tak.'' Urwa ne kaha ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke un aurton mein se jo us shart ka iqrar kar letin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey ke maine tum se bait ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sirf zaban se bait kartey they. qism Allah ki! bait kartey waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath ne kisi bhi aurat ke hath ko kabhi nahi chhuwaa, balke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sirf zaban se bait liya kartey they."
2714,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se har musalman ke sath khair-khahi karne ki shart par bait ki thi.
2715,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maine Namaz qaaim karne, zakat ada karne aur har musalman ke sath khair-khahi karne ki sharton ke sath bait ki thi."
2716,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne koi aisa khajoor ka baagh bechaa jiski pewand kaarii ho chuki thi to uska phal (is saal ke) bechney waley hi ka hoga. haan agar khareedaar shart laga de (to phal samet Sauda samjha jaaeyga).
2717,"Bareera, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan apni makaatibat ke barey mein unse madad leney ke liye aaein, unhon-ne abhi tak us mamley mein (apne maalikon ko) kuchh diya nahi tha. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unse farmaya ke apne maalikon ke yahan ja kar) unse malum karo) agar wo ye sura pasand karein ke tumhari makaatibat ki saari raqam mein ada kar dun aur tumhari 'walaa' mere liye ho jaey to main aisa kar sakti hun. Barira ne iska tazkira jab apne maalikon ke samney kya to unhon-ne inkar kya aur kaha ke wo (Aaisha (rz)) agar chaahein to ye kaare-sawaab tumharey sath kar sakti hain lekin 'walaa' to hamari hi rahegii. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne iska zikr Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke tum unhein khareed kar aazad kar do, 'walaa' to bahar-haal usi ki hoti hai jo aazad kar de."
2718,"wo (eik jang ke mauqe par) apne oont par Sawar aa rahe they, oont thak gaya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka udhar se guzar hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne oont ko aik zarb lagai aur uske haq mein dua farmai, chunanche oont itni tezi se chalney laga ke kabhi is tarah nahi chala tha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey aik auqiya mein mujhey bech do. maine inkar kya magar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke israar par phir maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath bech diya, lekin apne ghar tak is par sawari ki ijazat le li. phir jab ham (Madeena) pahunch gaey, to maine oont Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pesh kar diya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski qeemat bhi ada kar di, lekin jab main wapas honey laga to mere peechhey aik sahib ko mujhey bulaney ke liye bheja (main hazir hua to) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumhara oont koi ley thoda hi raha tha, apna oont ley jao, ye tumhara hi maal hai. (aur qeemat wapas nahi lii) Shoba ne Mughira ke waastey se bayan kya, unse Aamir ne aur unse Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina tak oont par mujhey sawar honey ki ijazat di thi, Ishaq ne Jarir se bayan kya aur unse Mughira ne ke) Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya thaa). isliye maine oont us shart par bech diya ke Madina pahunchne tak is par main sawar rahoonga. ata wghaira ne bayan kya ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha) is par Madina tak ki sawari tumhari hai. Muhammad-bin Munkadir ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kya ke unhon-ne Madina tak sawari ki shart lagai thi. Zaid-bin-Aslam ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ke waaste se bayan kya ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha) Madina tak is par tum hi rahogey. abu-Zubair ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kya ke Madina tak ki sawari ki Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey ijazat di thi. Aamash ne Salim se bayan kya aur unse Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke (rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya) apne ghar tak tum usi par Sawar ho ke jao. Ubaidullah aur ibne-Ishaq ne Wahab se bayan kya aur unse Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke oont ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik auqiya mein khareedaa tha. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Zaid-bin-Aslam ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se ki hai. ibne-Juraij ne ata wghaira se bayan kya aur unse Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne (ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha) main tumhara ye oont char Dinar mein leta hun, us hisab se ke aik Dinar das dirham ka hota hai, char Dinar ka aik auqiya hoga. Mughira ne Shabi ke waaste se aur unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se (unki riwayat mein aur). isi tarah ibne-Munkadir aur abu-Zubair ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se apni riwayat mein qeemat ka zikr nahi kya hai. Aamash ne Salim se aur unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se apni riwayat mein aik auqiya soney ki wazaahat ki hai. Abu-Ishaq ne Salim se aur unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se apni riwayat mein 200 dirham bayan kiye hain aur daawood-bin-Qais ne bayan kya, unse Ubaidullaah-bin-muqsim ne aur unse Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne oont Tabook ke rastey mein (jang se wapas hotey huey) khareedaa tha. mera khayal hai ke unhon-ne kaha ke char auqiya mein (khareedaa tha) abu-Nazara ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat mein bayan kya ke bees Dinar mein khareedaa tha. Shabi ke bayan ke mutabiq aik auqiya hi zyada riwayaton mein hai. isi tarah shart lagaanaa bhi zyada riwayaton se Sabit hai aur mere nazdeek sahi bhi yahi hai, ye abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne farmaayaa."
2719,"Ansar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney ( muwaakhaat ke baad) ye pesh kash! ki ke hamarey khajoor ke baghaat aap ham main aur hamarey bhaiyon ( muhajireen ( mein taqseem farma dein, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi. is par Ansar ne muhajireen se kaha ke aap log hamarey baaghon ke kaam kar diya karein aur hamarey sath phal mein Sharik ho jaaein, muhajireen ne kaha ke ham ne sun liya aur ham aisa hi karengey."
2720,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ki zameen yahudiyon ko us shart par di thi ke usmein kaam karein aur usey boein to aadhi paidawar unhein di jaya karegii.
2721,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''wo shartein jinke zariey tum ne aurton ki sharmgaahon ko halal kya hai, poori ki janey ki sabse zyada mustahiq hain.''"
2722,"ham aksar Ansar kheti kiya kartey they aur ham zameen batai par detey they. aksar aisa hota ke kisi khet ke aik tukdey mein paidawar hoti aur doosrey mein na hoti, isliye hamein us se mana kar diya gaya. lekin chandi (rupye wghaira) ke lagaan se mana nahi kya gaya."
2723,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''koii shehri kisi dehati ka maal tijarat na bechey. koi shakhs najash (dhokhadhadii) na karey aur na apne bhai ki lagai hui qeemat par bhaaw badhaaey. na koi shakhs apne kisi bhai ke paighaame-nikaah ki maujoodgii mein apna paigham bhejey aur na koi aurat (kisi mard se) apni behan ki talaaq ka mutalba karey (jo us mard ke nikah mein ho) taake is tarah uska hissey bhi khud ley ley.''
2724,"aik dehati sahabi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah! main aap se Allah ka waasta de kar kehta hun ke aap mera faisla kitabullah se kar dein. doosrey fareeq ne jo us se zyada samajh daar tha, kaha ke ji haan ! kitabullah se hi hamara faisla farmaiye, aur mujhey (apnaa muqaddima pesh karne ki) ijazat dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke pesh kar. us ne bayan karna shuru kya ke mera betaa in sahib ke yahan mazdoor tha. phir us ne inkii biwi se zina kar liya, jab mujhey malum hua ke (zinaa ki saza mein) mera ladka rajm (sangsaar) kar diya jaeyga to maine iske badley mein so bakriyan aur aik baandi di, phir ilm walon se iske barey mein puchha to unhon-ne bataya ke mere ladkey ko (zinaa ki saza mein kyonke wo ghair shadi shuda tha) so kode lagaey jaeinge aur aik saal ke liye Shahar badr kar diya jaeyga albatta uski biwi rajm (sangsaar) kar di jaeygi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''us zaat ki qasam! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, main tumhara faisla kitabullah hi se karunga. baandi aur bakriyan tumhen wapas milengii aur tumharey betey ko so kode lagaey jaeinge aur aik saal ke liye jalaa watan kya jaeyga achchha Anees! tum us aurat ke yahan jao, agar wo bhi) zina ka ( iqrar kar ley, to usey rajm (sangsaar) kar do (kyonke wo shadi shuda thi) bayan kya ke Anees (Raziallahu anhu) us aurat ke yahan gaey aur us ne iqrar kar liya, isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se wo rajm (sangsaar) ki gaii.''"
2725,"eik dehati sahabi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah! main aap se Allah ka waasta de kar kehta hun ke aap mera faisla kitabullah se kar dein. doosrey fareeq ne jo us se zyada samajh daar tha, kaha ke ji haan ! kitabullah se hi hamara faisla farmaiye, aur mujhey (apnaa muqaddima pesh karne ki) ijazat dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke pesh kar. us ne bayan karna shuru kya ke mera betaa in sahib ke yahan mazdoor tha. phir us ne inkii biwi se zina kar liya, jab mujhey malum hua ke (zinaa ki saza mein) mera ladka rajm (sangsaar) kar diya jaeyga to maine iske badley mein so bakriyan aur aik baandi di, phir ilm walon se iske barey mein puchha to unhon-ne bataya ke mere ladkey ko (zinaa ki saza mein kyonke wo ghair shadi shuda tha) so kode lagaey jaeinge aur aik saal ke liye Shahar badr kar diya jaeyga albatta uski biwi rajm (sangsaar) kar di jaeygi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''us zaat ki qasam! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, main tumhara faisla kitabullah hi se karunga. baandi aur bakriyan tumhen wapas milengii aur tumharey betey ko so kode lagaey jaeinge aur aik saal ke liye jalaa watan kya jaeyga achchha Anees! tum us aurat ke yahan jao, agar wo bhi) zina ka ( iqrar kar ley, to usey rajm (sangsaar) kar do (kyonke wo shadi shuda thi) bayan kya ke Anees (Raziallahu anhu) us aurat ke yahan gaey aur us ne iqrar kar liya, isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se wo rajm (sangsaar) ki gaii.''"
2726,"Barira (Raziallahu anhu) mere yahan aaiin, unhon-ne kitabat ka mamla kar liya tha. mujh se kehney lagiin ke aey ummul-momeneen! mujhey aap khareed lein, kyonke mere Malik mujhey bechney par aamada hain, phir aap mujhey aazad kar dena. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke haan, (main aisa kar loongii) lekin Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ne phir kaha ke mere Malik mujhey usi waqt bechengey jab wo 'walaa' ki shart apne liye laga lein. is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke phir mujhey zarurat nahi hai. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne suna, ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko malum hua (raawii ko shuba tha) to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ka kya mamla hai? tum unhein khareed kar aazad kar do, wo log jo chaahein shart laga lein. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke maine Barira ko khareed kar aazad kar diya aur uske Malik ne 'walaa' ki shart apne liye mehfooz rakhii. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi farmaya ke 'walaa' usi ki hoti hai jo aazad karey (doosrey ( jo chaahein shart lagaatey rahen."
2727,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (tijaaratii qaaflon ki) peshwai se mana farmaya tha aur us se bhi ke koi shehri kisi dehati ka saamaane-tijaarat bechey aur us se bhi ke koi aurat apni (deenii ya nasbii) behan ke talaaq ki shart lagaey aur us se ke koi apne kisi bhai ke bhaaw par bhaaw lagaaey, isi tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Najash (dhokhadhadii karkey bhaaw bhadhaaney) aur janwaron ka doodh unke thanon mein rokey rakhney se bhi mana farmaya Muhammad-bin-ar-ara ke sath us hadis ko Muaaz-bin-Muaaz aur Abdus-Samad bin Abdul-Waris ne bhi Shoba se riwayat kya hai aur ghandar aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne yun kaha ke manaahii ki gaee thi. Aadam-bin-abii-Ayaas ne yun kaha ke hamein mana kya gaya tha nazar aur hujjaaj-bin-Minhaal ne yun kaha ke mana kya tha (rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne)."
2728,"ham Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir they. unhon-ne kaha ke mujh se Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''khizr se jo ja kar miley they wo Musa (Alaihissalam) they.'' phir aakhir tak hadis bayan ki ke khizr (Alaihissalam) ne Musa (Alaihissalam) se kaha kya main aapko pahley hi nahi bata chuka tha ke aap mere sath sabr nahi kar saktey (Moosaa (Alaihissalam) ki taraf se) pahlaa sawal to bhool kar hua tha, beech ka shart ke taur par aur tesraa jaan-bojh kar hua tha. aap ne khizr se kaha tha ke ''main jisko bhool gaya aap usmein mujh se muaakhza na kijiye aur na mera kaam mushkil banaaiye.'' donon ko aik ladka mila jisey khizr (Alaihissalam) ne qatl kar diya wo aagey badhey to unhein aik diwar mili jo girney wali thi lekin khizr (Alaihissalam) ne usey durust kar diyaa."
2729,"mere paas Barira (Raziallahu anhu) aaein aur kehney lagiin ke maine apne Malik se nau (9) auqiya chandi par makaatibat kar li hai, har saal aik auqiya dena hoga. aap bhi meri madad keejiye. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke agar tumharey Malik chaahein to main aik dam unhein itni qeemat ada kar sakti hun. lekin tumhari 'walaa' meri hogi. Barira (Raziallahu anhu) apne maalikon ke yahan gain aur unse is sura ka zikr kya lekin unhon-ne 'walaa' ke liye inkar kya. jab wo unke yahan se wapas huin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi tashrif farma they. unhon-ne kaha ke maine apne maalikon ke samney ye sura rakhi thi, lekin wo kehtey they ke 'walaa' unhiin ki hogi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi ye baat suni aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko soorate-haal se aagah kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke to unhein khareed ley aur unhein 'walaa' ki shart lagaaney de. 'walaa' to usi ke sath qaaim ho sakti hai jo aazad kare. chunanche Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne aisa hi kya phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sahaba mein gaey aur Allah Taala ki hamd w sana ke baad farmaya ke kuchh logon ko kya ho gaya hai ke wo aisi shartein lagaatey hain jinka koi pata (sanad, daleel) kitabullah mein nahi hai aisi koi bhi shart jiska pata (sanad, daleel) kitabullah mein na ho baatil hai chahe so shartein kyon na laga li jaaein. Allah ka faisla hi haq hai aur Allah ki shartein hi paayedaar hain aur 'walaa' to usi ko milegii jo aazad karega."
2730,"jab unke hath paon khaibar walon ne tod daley to umr (Raziallahu anhu) khutba dene ke liye khadey huey, aap (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab khaibar ke yahudiyon se unki jaaidaad ka mamla kya tha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke jab tak Allah Taala tumhen qaaim rakhey ham bhi qaaim rakhengey aur Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) wahan apne amwaal ke silsiley mein gaey to raat mein unke sath maar-peet ka mamla kya gaya jis se unke paon toot gaey. khaibar mein unke siwa aur koi hamara dushman nahi, wahi hamarey dushman hain aur unhiin par hamein shubah hai isliye main unhein jilaa-watan kar dena hi munasib janta hun. jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne iska pukhta irada kar liya to banu-abii-Huqaiq (eik Yahudi khaandaan) ka aik shakhs tha, aaya aur kaha ya ameerul-momineen kya aap hamein jilaa-watan kar dengey halanke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein yahan baqi rakha tha aur ham se jaaidaad ka aik mamla bhi kya tha aur uski hamein khaibar mein rehney dene ki shart bhi aap ne lagai thi. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par farmaya kya tum ye samajhtey ho ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka farman bhool gaya hun. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kaha tha ke tumhara kya haal hoga jab tum khaibar se nikaley jaogey aur tumharey oont tumhen raaton-raat liye phirengey. usne kaha ye abul-Qaasim (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ka aik mazaaq tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Allah ke dushman! tum ne jhooti baat kahi. chunanche umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein Shahar badr kar diya aur unke phalon ki kuchh naqd qeemat kuchh maal aur oont aur doosrey saman yani kajaawey aur rassiyon ki sura mein ada kar di. uski riwayat Hammaad-bin-Salma ne Ubaidullah se naql ki hai jaisa ke mujhey yaqin hai Naafe se aur unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mukhtasar taur par."
2731,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par (Makka) ja rahe they, abhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rastey hi mein they, farmaya Khalid-bin Waleed Quraish ke) 200 ( sawaaron ke sath hamari naql w harkat ka andaza lagaaney ke liye maqaame-Ghameem mein muqeem hai (ye Quraish ka muqaddimatul-jaish (main army) hai) isliye tum log dahini taraf se jao, to Allah ki qism Khalid ko unke mutaalliq kuchh bhi ilm na ho saka aur jab unhon-ne us lashkar ka ghubaar uthtaa hua dekha to Quraish ko jaldi-jaldi khabar dene gaey. idhar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chaltey rahe yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us ghaati par pahunchey jis se Makka mein utartey hain to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari baith gaee. sahaba ontni ko uthaney ke liye hal-hal kehney lagey lekin wo apni jagah se na uthii. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke qaswaa ad gaee Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya qaswaa Adi nahi aur na ye uski aadat hai, isey to us zaat ne rok liya jisne haathiyon (ke lashakr) ko (Makka) mein dakhil honey se rok liya tha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai Quraish jo bhi aisa mutalba rakhengey jis mein Allah ki haram ki hui chizon ki badaai ho to main uska mutalba manzoor kar loonga. aakhir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ontni ko daantaa to wo uth gaee. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sahaba se aagey nikal gaey aur Hudaibiya ke aakhiri kinarey Samad (eik chashma ya garhaa) par jahan pani kam tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne padao kya. log thoda thodaa pani istemal karne lagey, unhon-ne pani ko thaharney hi nahi diya, sab kheench dala. ab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se piyaas ki shikayat ki gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne tarkash mein se aik teer nikal kar diya ke us garhey mein daal dein b-khudaa teer gaadtey hi pani unhein sairaab karne ke liye ubalney laga aur wo log poori tarah sairaab ho gaey. log usi haal mein they ke Budail-bin-Warqaa Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) apni qaum khuza'aa ke kai aadmiyon ko lekar hazir hua. ye log tahaama ke rehney waley they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke mahrame-raaz badey khair-khaah they. unhon-ne khabar di ke main Ka'b-bin-Looii aur Aamir-bin-Looii ko peechhey chhod kar aa raha hun. jinhoney Hudaibiya ke pani ke zakheeron par apna padao daal diya hai, unke sath kasrat se doodh dene wali oontniyan apne naey-naey bachchon ke sath hain. wo aap se ladengey aur aap ke Baitullah pahunchne mein rukawat banengey. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ham kisi se ladney nahi aaey hain sirf Umra ke iraadey se aaey hain aur waqia to ye hai (musalsal ladaaiyon) ne Quraish ko bhi kamzor kar diya hai aur unhein bada nuqsan uthana padaa hai, ab agar wo chaahein to main aik muddat unse suleh ka muaahida kar loonga, us arse mein wo mere aur Awam (kuffaar mushrekeene-arab) ke darmyan na padein phir agar main kaamyaab ho jaun aur (uske baad) wo chaahein to is Deen (Islam) mein wo bhi dakhil ho saktey hain (jis main aur tamam log dakhil ho chukey hongey) lekin agar mujhey kamiyabi nahi hui to unhein bhi aaraam mil jaeyga aur agar unhein meri pesh-kash se inkar hai to us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai jab tak mera sar tan se juda nahi ho jata, main is Deen ke liye barabar ladtaa rahunga ya phir Allah Taala usey laagu hi farma dega. Budail (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Quraish tak aap ki guftgu mein pohchaaunga, chunanche wo wapas huey aur Quraish ke yahan pahunchey aur kaha ke ham tumharey paas us shakhs (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ke yahan se aa rahe hain aur ham ne usey aik baat kehtey suna hai, agar tum chaho to tumharey samney usey bayan kar saktey hain. Quraish ke be-waqufon ne kaha ke hamein uski zarurat nahi ke tum us shakhs ki koi baat hamein sunao. jo log saahibur-Raaey they, unhon-ne kaha ke theek hai jo kuchh tum ne suna hai ham se bayan kar do. unhon-ne kaha ke maine usey (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ko ye kehtey suna hai aur phir jo kuchh unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha, sab bayan kar diya. is par Urwa-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) (jo us waqt tak kuffaar ke sath they) khadey huey aur kaha aey qaum ke logo ! kya tum mujh par bap ki tarah shafqat nahi rakhtey. sab ne kaha kyon nahi, zaroor rakhtey hain. Mina Urwa ne phir kaha kya main betey ki tarah tumhara khair-khaah nahi hun, unhon-ne kaha kyon nahi. Urwa ne phir kaha tum log mujh par kisi qism ki tohmat laga saktey ho? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. unhon-ne puchha kya tumhen malum nahi hai ke maine Ukaaz walon ko tumhari madad ke liye kaha tha aur jab unhon-ne inkar kya to maine apne gharaaney, aulad aur un tamam logon ko tumharey paas la kar khada kar diya tha jinhoney mera kehna maanaa tha? Quraish ne kaha kyon nahi (aap ki baatein durust hain) iske baad unhon-ne kaha dekho ab us shakhs (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ne tumharey samney aik achi tajwiz rakhi hai, usey tum qabool kar lo aur mujhey uske paas ( guftgu (ke liye janey do, sab ne kaha aap zaroor jaaiye. chunanche Urwa-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se guftgu shuru ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse bhi wahi baatein kahin jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Budail se keh chukey they, Urwa (Raziallahu anhu) ne us waqt kaha, aey Muhammad (sl)! bataiye agar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni qaum ko tabah kar diya to kya apne se pahley kisi bhi Arab ke mutaalliq suna hai ke usne apne khandan ka naam w nishan mitaa diya ho lekin agar dusri baat waaqe hui (yani ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par ghalib huey) to main Allah ki qism tumharey sathiyon ka munh dekhta hun ye mukhtalif jinson k log yahi karengey. us waqt ye sab log bhag jaeinge aur aapko tanha chhod dengey. is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) boley ( امصص بظر اللات ( . kya ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se bhag jaeinge aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko tanha chhod dengey. Urwa ne puchha kon sahib hain? logon ne bataya ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hain. Urwa ne kaha us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai agar tumhara mujh par aik ehsan na hota jiska ab tak mein badla nahi de saka hun to tumhen zaroor jawab deta. bayan kya ke wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se phir guftgu karne lagey aur guftgu kartey huey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dadhi Mubarak pakad liya kartey they. Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas khadey they, talwaar latkaey huey aur sar par khud pahney. Urwa jab bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dadhi Mubarak ki taraf apna hath ley jatey to Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) talwaar ki niyaam ko iske hath par maartey aur unse kehtey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dadhi se apna hath alag rakh. Urwa (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna sar uthaya aur puchha ye kon sahib hain? logon ne bataya ke Mugheera-bin-Sho'ba. Urwa ne unhein mukhaatab karke kaha aey daghaa baaz! kya maine teri daghaa bazi ki saza se tujh ko nahi bachaayaa? asl mein Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) (Islam laney se pahley) jahiliyat mein aik qaum ke sath rahe they phir un sab ko qatl karke unka maal ley liya tha. iske baad (Madina ( aaey aur Islam ke halqa bagosh ho gaey (to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein unka maal bhi rakh diya ke jo chaahein iske mutaalliq hukm farmaaein) lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke tera Islam to main qabool karta hun, raha ye maal to mera us se koi waasta nahi. kyonke wo daghaa bazi se hath aaya hai jisey main ley nahi sakta, phir Urwa (Raziallahu anhu) ghoor-ghoor kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab ki naql w harkat dekhtey rahe. phir rawi ne bayan kya ke qism Allah ki agar kabhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne balgham bhi thooka to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab ne apne hathon par usey ley liya aur usey apne chehre aur badan par mal liya. kisi kaam ka agar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya to uski bajaa aawrii mein aik doosrey se aagey badh janey ki koshish kartey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wuzu karne lagey to aisa malum hua ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wuzu ke pani par ladai ho jaeygi (yani har shakhs us pani ko leney ki koshish karta tha) jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) guftgu karne lagey to sab par khamoshi chhaa jati. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ta'zeem ka ye haal tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathi nazar bhar kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh bhi nahi saktey they. khair Urwa jab apne sathiyon se ja kar miley to unse kaha aey logo! qism Allah ki main baadshaahon ke darbar mein bhi wafad lekar gaya hon, qaisar w Kisraa aur Najashi sab ke darbar mein lekin Allah ki qism maine kabhi nahi dekha ke kisi badshah ke sathi uski us darja ta'zeem kartey hon jitni Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ta'zeem kartey hain. qism Allah ki agar Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne balgham bhi thook diya to unke ashaab ne usey apne hathon mein ley liya aur usey apne chehra aur badan par mil liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein agar koi hukm diya to har shakhs ne usey bajaa laney mein aik doosrey par sabqat ki koshish ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne agar wuzu kya to aisa malum hota ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wuzu par ladai ho jaeygi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab guftgu shuru ki to har taraf khamoshi chhaa gaee. unke dilon mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ta'zeem ka ye aalim tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko nazar bhar kar bhi nahi dekh saktey. unhon-ne tumharey samney aik bhalii sura rakhi hai, tumhen chahiye ke usey qabool kar lo. is par banu-kinaana ka aik shakhs bola ke achchha mujhey bhi unke yahan janey do, logon ne kaha tum bhi ja saktey ho. jab ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab (Raziallahu anhu) ke qareeb pahunchey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye falan shakhs hai, aik aisi qaum ka fard jo Baitullah ki qurbani ke janwaron ki ta'zeem kartey hain. isliye qurbani ke janwar iske samney kar do. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne qurbani ke janwar iske samney kar diye aur labbaik kehtey huey uska istiqbaal kya jab us ne ye manzar dekha to kehney laga ke Subhan-Allah hargiz munasib nahi hai ke aisey logon ko Kaba se rokaa jaey. iske baad Quraish mein se aik doosra shakhs Makooz-bin-Hafs naam ke khada hua aur kehney laga ke mujhey bhi unke yahan janey do. sab ne kaha ke tum bhi ja saktey ho jab wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) se qareeb hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye Makooz hai aik badtareen shakhs hai. phir wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se guftgu karne laga. abhi wo guftgu kar hi raha tha ke Suhail-bin-Amr aa gaya. Mina Mamar ne (pichhli sanad ke saath) bayan kya ke mujhey Ayub ne khabar di aur unhein Ikrima ne ke jab Suhail-bin-Amr aaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (nek faalii ke taur par) farmaya tumhara mamla aasan (Sahal) ho gaya. Mamar ne bayan kya ke Zohri ne apni hadis mein is tarah bayan kya tha ke jab Suhail-bin-Amr aaya to kehney laga ke hamarey aur apne darmyan (Suleh ( ki aik tahreer likh lo. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kaatib ko bulwaya aur farmaya ke likho ( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم ( Suhel kehney laga Rehman ko Allah ki qism main nahi janta ke wo kya cheez hai. albatta tum yun likh saktey ho باسمك اللهم‏ jaisey pahley likha kartey they. musalmanon ne kaha ke qism Allah ki hamein ( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم (ke siwa aur koi doosra jumla na likhnaa chahiye lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke باسمك اللهم‏ hii likhney do. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne likhwaayaa ye Muhammad Rasulullah ki taraf se suleh naamaa ki dastaawez hai. Suhel ne kaha agar hamein ye malum hota ke aap Rasulullah hain to na ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Kaba se roktey aur na aap se jang kartey. aap to sirf itna likhiye ke ''Muhammad-bin-Abdullaah'' is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Allah gawah hai ke main uska sachcha rasool hun chahe tum mujhe jhutlaatey raho. likho ji ''Muhammad-bin-Abdullaah'' Zohri ne bayan kya ke ye sab kuchh (narmii aur riaayat) sirf Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us irshad ka nateeja tha (jo pahley Budail (Raziallahu anhu) se keh chukey they) ke Quraish mujh se jo bhi aisa mutalba karengey jis se Allah Taala ki hurmaton ki ta'zeem maqsud hogi to main unke mutaalbey ko zaroor maan loonga, isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Suhel se farmaya lekin suleh ke liye pehli shart ye hogi ke tum log hamein Baitullah ke tawaaf karne ke liye janey doge. Suhel ne kaha qism Allah ki ham (is saal) aisa nahi honey dengey warna Arab kahengey ham maghloob ho gaey they (is liye ham ne ijazat de di) aainda saal ke liye ijazat hai. chunanche ye bhi likh liya. phir Suhel ne likha ke ye shart bhi (likh liijiye) ke hamari taraf ka jo shakhs bhi aap ke yahan jaeyga chahe wo aap ke Deen hi par kyon na ho aap usey hamein wapas kar dengey. musalmanon ne (ye shart sun kar kaha) sub'haan-Allaah! (eik shakhs ko) mushrikon ke hawale kis tarah kya ja sakta hai jo musalman ho kar aaya ho. abhi yahi baatein ho rahi thin ke abu-Jandal bin Suhail-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) apni bediyon ko ghaseet'tey huey aa pahunchey, wo Makka ke nashebii ilaaqey ki taraf se bhaagey they aur ab khud ko musalmanon ke samney daal diya tha. Suhel ne kaha aey Muhammad! ye pahlaa shakhs hai jiske liye (suleh naamaa ke mutaabiq) main mutalba karta hun ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein usey wapas kar dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke abhi to ham ne (suleh naame ki is baat ko) suleh naamaa mein likha bhi nahi hai (is liye jab suleh naamaa tay pa jaeyga uske baad isko laagu hona chaahiye) Suhel kehney laga ke Allah ki qism phir main kisi buniyad par bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suleh nahi karunga. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya achchha mujh par us aik ko de kar ehsan kar do. usne kaha ke main is silsiley mein ehsan bhi nahi kar sakta. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi hamein ehsan kar dena chahiye lekin us ne yahi jawab diya ke main aisa kabhi nahi kar sakta. albatta makooz ne kaha ke chaliye ham iska Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par ehsan kartey hain magar (uski baat nahi chalii) abu-Jandal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha muslmaanon! main musalman ho kar aaya hun. kya mujhey mushrikon ke hath mein de diya jaaeyga? kya mere sath jo aziyatein pahunchai gain thin. rawi ne bayan kya ke Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha aakhir main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya, kya ye waqia aur haqiqat nahi ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke Nabi hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kyon nahi ! maine arz kya, kya ham haq par nahi hain aur kya hamarey dushman baatil par nahi hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kyon nahi ! maine kaha phir apne Deen ke mamley mein kyon dabein . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya main Allah ka rasool hon, uske hukm ki nafarmani nahi kar sakta aur wahi mera madadgaar hai. maine kaha kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ham se ye nahi farmatey they ke ham Baitullah jaeinge aur uska tawaaf karengey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke theek hai lekin kya maine tum se ye kaha tha ke isi saal ham Baitullah pahunch jaengey. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine kaha nahi (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us qaid ke sath nahi farmaya tha) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir usmein koi shuba nahi ke tum Baitullah tak zaroor pahuncho gey aur aik din iska tawaaf karogey. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaya aur unse bhi yahi puchha ke abu-Bakar! kya ye haqiqat nahi ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke Nabi hain? unhon-ne bhi kaha ke kyon nahi. maine puchha kya ham haq par nahi hain? aur kya hamarey dushman baatil par nahi hain? unhon-ne kaha kyon nahin! maine kaha ke phir apne Deen ko kyon zaleel karein? Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : janaab! bila shak w shuba wo Allah ke rasool hain, aur apne rab ke hukm ki nafarmani nahi kar saktey aur rab hi unka madadgaar hai. to unki rassii mazbootii se pakad lo, Allah gawah hai ke wo haq par hain. Mina maine kaha kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ham se ye nahi kehtey they ke an-qareeb ham Baitullah pahunchengey aur iska tawaaf karengey unhon-ne farmaya ke ye bhi sahi hai lekin kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aap se ye farmaya tha ke usi saal aap Baitullah pahunch jaengey. maine kaha ke nahi. phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha phir usmein bhi koi shak w shuba nahi ke aap aik na aik din Baitullah pahunchengey aur uska tawaaf karengey. Zohri ne bayan kya ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya baad mein maine apni jald bazi ki bharpaaii ke liye nek aamaal kiye. phir jab suleh naame se aap farigh ho chukey to sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke ab utho aur (jin janwaron ko sath laey ho unkii) qurbani kar lo aur sar bhi mundwaa lo. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Allah gawah hai sahaba mein se aik shakhs bhi na utha aur teen martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye jumla farmaya. jab koi na utha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Umme-Salma ke kheme mein gaey aur unse logon ke tarze-amal ka zikr kya. Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha aey Allah ke nabii! kya aap ye pasand karengey ke bahar tashrif ley jayen aur kisi se kuchh na kahin balke apna qurbani ka janwar zabah kar lein aur apne hajjaam ko bula lein jo aap ke baal moond de. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey. kisi se kuchh nahi kaha aur sab kuchh kya, apne janwar ki qurbani kar li aur apne hajjaam ko bulwaya jisne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baal moondey. jab sahaba ne dekha to wo bhi aik doosrey ke baal moondney lagey, aisa malum hota tha ke ranj w gham mein aik doosrey se lad padeingey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas (Makka se) chand momin auratein aaein to Allah Taala ne ye hukm nazil farmaya (ya أيها الذين آمنوا إذا جاءكم المؤمنات مهاجرات فامتحنوهن‏ (aey logo! jo eman la chukey ho jab tumharey paas momin auratein hijrat karke aaein to unka imtihaan ley ( بعصم الكوافر‏ ( tak. us din umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni 2 beeviyon ko talaaq di jo ab tak musalman na hui thin. unmein se aik ne to Muaawiya-bin-Abii-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anhu) se nikah kar liya tha aur dusri se Safwaan-bin-Umayya ne. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina wapas tashrif laey to Quraish ke aik fard Abu-Baseer (Raziallahu anhu) (Makka se faraar ho kar) hazir huey. wo musalman ho chukey they. Quraish ne unhein wapas leney ke liye 2 aadmiyon ko bheja aur unhon-ne aa kar kaha ke hamarey sath aap ka muaahida ho chuka hai. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abu-Baseer (Raziallahu anhu) ko wapas kar diya. Quraish ke donon afraad jab unhein wapas lekar lautey aur zul-Hulaifa pahunchey to khajoor khaney ke liye utrey jo unke sath thi. Abu-Baseer (Raziallahu anhu) ne unmein se aik se farmaya qism Allah ki tumhari talwaar bahut achi malum hoti hai. doosrey sathi ne talwaar niyaam se nikal di. us shakhs ne kaha haan Allah ki qism bahut hi zyada umda talwaar hai, main iska bahut baar tajriba kar chuka hun. Abu-Baseer (Raziallahu anhu) is par boley ke zara mujhey bhi to dikhao aur is tarah apne qabze mein kar liya phir us shakhs ne talwaar ke Malik ko aisi zarb lagai ke wo wahin thanda ho gaya. uska doosra sathi bhag kar Madina aaya aur masjid mein daudta hua dakhil hua Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab usey dekha to farmaya ye shakhs kuchh khof-zada malum hota hai. jab wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb pahuncha to kehney laga Allah ki qism mera sathi to maara gaya aur main bhi maara jaaunga (agar aap logon ne Abu-Baseer ko na rokaa) itney mein Abu-Baseer bhi aagey aur arz kya aey Allah ke Nabi ! Allah ki qism Allah Taala ne aap ki zimme-dari poori kar di, aap mujhey unke hawale kar chukey they lekin Allah Taala ne mujhey unse nijat dilaaii. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (teri maa ki kharaabii) agar iska koi aik bhi madadgaar hota to phir ladai ke sholey bhadak uthtey. jab unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ye alfaz suney to samajh gaey ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) phir kuffaar ke hawale kar dengey isliye wahan se nikal gaey aur samandar ke kinarey par aa gaey. rawi ne bayan kya ke apne ghar walon (Makka se) chhoot kar abu-jandal-bin-Suhail (Raziallahu anhu) bhi Abu-Baseer (Raziallahu anhu) se ja miley aur ab ye haal tha ke Quraish ka jo shakhs bhi Islam laataa (bajaaey Madina aaney ke) Abu-Baseer (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan (saahile-samandar par) chala jata. is tarah se aik jamat bin gaee aur Allah gawah hai ye log Quraish ke jis qafley ke mutaalliq bhi sun letey ke wo Sham (Syria) ja raha hai to usey rastey hi mein rok kar loot letey aur qaafila walon ko qatl kar detey. ab Quraish ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan Allah aur raham ka waasta de kar darkhaast bheji ke aap kisi ko bhejiin (Abu-Baseer (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke doosrey sathiyon ke yahan ke wo Quraish ko takleefein dene se ruk jaaein) aur uske baad jo shakhs bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan jaeyga (Makka se) usey amn hai. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke yahan apna aadmi bheja aur Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaaii وهو الذي كف أيديهم عنكم وأيديكم عنهم ببطن مكة من بعد أن أظفركم عليهم‏''aur wo zaat parwardigar jisne rok diya tha tumharey hathon ko unse aur unke hathon ko tum se (yani jang nahi ho saki thi) wadi Makka mein (Hudaibiya mein) baad mein iske ke tum ko ghalib kar diya tha un par yahan tak ke baat jahiliyat ke daur ki be-jaa himaayat tak pahunch gaee thii).'' unki hamiiyat ( jahiliyat ( ye thi ke unhon-ne (muaahidey mein bhi) aap ke liye Allah ke Nabi honey ka iqrar nahi kya isi tarah unhon-ne ( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم ( nahi likhney diya aur aap Baitullah janey se rukey rahey."
2732,"rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par (Makka) ja rahe they, abhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rastey hi mein they, farmaya Khalid-bin Waleed Quraish ke) 200 ( sawaaron ke sath hamari naql w harkat ka andaza lagaaney ke liye maqaame-Ghameem mein muqeem hai (ye Quraish ka muqaddimatul-jaish (main army) hai) isliye tum log dahini taraf se jao, to Allah ki qism Khalid ko unke mutaalliq kuchh bhi ilm na ho saka aur jab unhon-ne us lashkar ka ghubaar uthtaa hua dekha to Quraish ko jaldi-jaldi khabar dene gaey. idhar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chaltey rahe yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us ghaati par pahunchey jis se Makka mein utartey hain to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari baith gaee. sahaba ontni ko uthaney ke liye hal-hal kehney lagey lekin wo apni jagah se na uthii. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke qaswaa ad gaee Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya qaswaa Adi nahi aur na ye uski aadat hai, isey to us zaat ne rok liya jisne haathiyon (ke lashakr) ko (Makka) mein dakhil honey se rok liya tha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai Quraish jo bhi aisa mutalba rakhengey jis mein Allah ki haram ki hui chizon ki badaai ho to main uska mutalba manzoor kar loonga. aakhir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ontni ko daantaa to wo uth gaee. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sahaba se aagey nikal gaey aur Hudaibiya ke aakhiri kinarey Samad (eik chashma ya garhaa) par jahan pani kam tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne padao kya. log thoda thodaa pani istemal karne lagey, unhon-ne pani ko thaharney hi nahi diya, sab kheench dala. ab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se piyaas ki shikayat ki gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne tarkash mein se aik teer nikal kar diya ke us garhey mein daal dein b-khudaa teer gaadtey hi pani unhein sairaab karne ke liye ubalney laga aur wo log poori tarah sairaab ho gaey. log usi haal mein they ke Budail-bin-Warqaa Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) apni qaum khuza'aa ke kai aadmiyon ko lekar hazir hua. ye log tahaama ke rehney waley they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke mahrame-raaz badey khair-khaah they. unhon-ne khabar di ke main Ka'b-bin-Looii aur Aamir-bin-Looii ko peechhey chhod kar aa raha hun. jinhoney Hudaibiya ke pani ke zakheeron par apna padao daal diya hai, unke sath kasrat se doodh dene wali oontniyan apne naey-naey bachchon ke sath hain. wo aap se ladengey aur aap ke Baitullah pahunchne mein rukawat banengey. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ham kisi se ladney nahi aaey hain sirf Umra ke iraadey se aaey hain aur waqia to ye hai (musalsal ladaaiyon) ne Quraish ko bhi kamzor kar diya hai aur unhein bada nuqsan uthana padaa hai, ab agar wo chaahein to main aik muddat unse suleh ka muaahida kar loonga, us arse mein wo mere aur Awam (kuffaar mushrekeene-arab) ke darmyan na padein phir agar main kaamyaab ho jaun aur (uske baad) wo chaahein to is Deen (Islam) mein wo bhi dakhil ho saktey hain (jis main aur tamam log dakhil ho chukey hongey) lekin agar mujhey kamiyabi nahi hui to unhein bhi aaraam mil jaeyga aur agar unhein meri pesh-kash se inkar hai to us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai jab tak mera sar tan se juda nahi ho jata, main is Deen ke liye barabar ladtaa rahunga ya phir Allah Taala usey laagu hi farma dega. Budail (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Quraish tak aap ki guftgu mein pohchaaunga, chunanche wo wapas huey aur Quraish ke yahan pahunchey aur kaha ke ham tumharey paas us shakhs (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ke yahan se aa rahe hain aur ham ne usey aik baat kehtey suna hai, agar tum chaho to tumharey samney usey bayan kar saktey hain. Quraish ke be-waqufon ne kaha ke hamein uski zarurat nahi ke tum us shakhs ki koi baat hamein sunao. jo log saahibur-Raaey they, unhon-ne kaha ke theek hai jo kuchh tum ne suna hai ham se bayan kar do. unhon-ne kaha ke maine usey (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ko ye kehtey suna hai aur phir jo kuchh unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha, sab bayan kar diya. is par Urwa-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) (jo us waqt tak kuffaar ke sath they) khadey huey aur kaha aey qaum ke logo ! kya tum mujh par bap ki tarah shafqat nahi rakhtey. sab ne kaha kyon nahi, zaroor rakhtey hain. Urwa ne phir kaha kya main betey ki tarah tumhara khair-khaah nahi hun, unhon-ne kaha kyon nahi. Urwa ne phir kaha tum log mujh par kisi qism ki tohmat laga saktey ho? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. unhon-ne puchha kya tumhen malum nahi hai ke maine Ukaaz walon ko tumhari madad ke liye kaha tha aur jab unhon-ne inkar kya to maine apne gharaaney, aulad aur un tamam logon ko tumharey paas la kar khada kar diya tha jinhoney mera kehna maanaa tha? Quraish ne kaha kyon nahi (aap ki baatein durust hain) iske baad unhon-ne kaha dekho ab us shakhs (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ne tumharey samney aik achi tajwiz rakhi hai, usey tum qabool kar lo aur mujhey uske paas ( guftgu (ke liye janey do, sab ne kaha aap zaroor jaaiye. chunanche Urwa-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se guftgu shuru ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse bhi wahi baatein kahin jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Budail se keh chukey they, Urwa (Raziallahu anhu) ne us waqt kaha, aey Muhammad (sl)! bataiye agar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni qaum ko tabah kar diya to kya apne se pahley kisi bhi Arab ke mutaalliq suna hai ke usne apne khandan ka naam w nishan mitaa diya ho lekin agar dusri baat waaqe hui (yani ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par ghalib huey) to main Allah ki qism tumharey sathiyon ka munh dekhta hun ye mukhtalif jinson k log yahi karengey. us waqt ye sab log bhag jaeinge aur aapko tanha chhod dengey. is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) boley ( امصص بظر اللات ( . kya ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se bhag jaeinge aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko tanha chhod dengey. Urwa ne puchha kon sahib hain? logon ne bataya ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hain. Urwa ne kaha us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai agar tumhara mujh par aik ehsan na hota jiska ab tak mein badla nahi de saka hun to tumhen zaroor jawab deta. bayan kya ke wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se phir guftgu karne lagey aur guftgu kartey huey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dadhi Mubarak pakad liya kartey they. Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas khadey they, talwaar latkaey huey aur sar par khud pahney. Urwa jab bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dadhi Mubarak ki taraf apna hath ley jatey to Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) talwaar ki niyaam ko iske hath par maartey aur unse kehtey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dadhi se apna hath alag rakh. Urwa (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna sar uthaya aur puchha ye kon sahib hain? logon ne bataya ke Mugheera-bin-Sho'ba. Urwa ne unhein mukhaatab karke kaha aey daghaa baaz! kya maine teri daghaa bazi ki saza se tujh ko nahi bachaayaa? asl mein Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) (Islam laney se pahley) jahiliyat mein aik qaum ke sath rahe they phir un sab ko qatl karke unka maal ley liya tha. iske baad (Madina ( aaey aur Islam ke halqa bagosh ho gaey (to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein unka maal bhi rakh diya ke jo chaahein iske mutaalliq hukm farmaaein) lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke tera Islam to main qabool karta hun, raha ye maal to mera us se koi waasta nahi. kyonke wo daghaa bazi se hath aaya hai jisey main ley nahi sakta, phir Urwa (Raziallahu anhu) ghoor-ghoor kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab ki naql w harkat dekhtey rahe. phir rawi ne bayan kya ke qism Allah ki agar kabhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne balgham bhi thooka to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab ne apne hathon par usey ley liya aur usey apne chehre aur badan par mal liya. kisi kaam ka agar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya to uski bajaa aawrii mein aik doosrey se aagey badh janey ki koshish kartey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wuzu karne lagey to aisa malum hua ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wuzu ke pani par ladai ho jaeygi (yani har shakhs us pani ko leney ki koshish karta tha) jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) guftgu karne lagey to sab par khamoshi chhaa jati. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ta'zeem ka ye haal tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathi nazar bhar kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh bhi nahi saktey they. khair Urwa jab apne sathiyon se ja kar miley to unse kaha aey logo! qism Allah ki main baadshaahon ke darbar mein bhi wafad lekar gaya hon, qaisar w Kisraa aur Najashi sab ke darbar mein lekin Allah ki qism maine kabhi nahi dekha ke kisi badshah ke sathi uski us darja ta'zeem kartey hon jitni Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ta'zeem kartey hain. qism Allah ki agar Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne balgham bhi thook diya to unke ashaab ne usey apne hathon mein ley liya aur usey apne chehra aur badan par mil liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein agar koi hukm diya to har shakhs ne usey bajaa laney mein aik doosrey par sabqat ki koshish ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne agar wuzu kya to aisa malum hota ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wuzu par ladai ho jaeygi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab guftgu shuru ki to har taraf khamoshi chhaa gaee. unke dilon mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ta'zeem ka ye aalim tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko nazar bhar kar bhi nahi dekh saktey. unhon-ne tumharey samney aik bhalii sura rakhi hai, tumhen chahiye ke usey qabool kar lo. is par banu-kinaana ka aik shakhs bola ke achchha mujhey bhi unke yahan janey do, logon ne kaha tum bhi ja saktey ho. jab ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab (Raziallahu anhu) ke qareeb pahunchey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye falan shakhs hai, aik aisi qaum ka fard jo Baitullah ki qurbani ke janwaron ki ta'zeem kartey hain. isliye qurbani ke janwar iske samney kar do. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne qurbani ke janwar iske samney kar diye aur labbaik kehtey huey uska istiqbaal kya jab us ne ye manzar dekha to kehney laga ke Subhan-Allah hargiz munasib nahi hai ke aisey logon ko Kaba se rokaa jaey. iske baad Quraish mein se aik doosra shakhs Makooz-bin-Hafs naam ke khada hua aur kehney laga ke mujhey bhi unke yahan janey do. sab ne kaha ke tum bhi ja saktey ho jab wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) se qareeb hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye Makooz hai aik badtareen shakhs hai. phir wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se guftgu karne laga. abhi wo guftgu kar hi raha tha ke Suhail-bin-Amr aa gaya. Mamar ne (pichhli sanad ke saath) bayan kya ke mujhey Ayub ne khabar di aur unhein Ikrima ne ke jab Suhail-bin-Amr aaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (nek faalii ke taur par) farmaya tumhara mamla aasan (Sahal) ho gaya. Mamar ne bayan kya ke Zohri ne apni hadis mein is tarah bayan kya tha ke jab Suhail-bin-Amr aaya to kehney laga ke hamarey aur apne darmyan (Suleh ( ki aik tahreer likh lo. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kaatib ko bulwaya aur farmaya ke likho ( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم ( Suhel kehney laga Rehman ko Allah ki qism main nahi janta ke wo kya cheez hai. albatta tum yun likh saktey ho باسمك اللهم‏ jaisey pahley likha kartey they. musalmanon ne kaha ke qism Allah ki hamein ( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم (ke siwa aur koi doosra jumla na likhnaa chahiye lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke باسمك اللهم‏ hii likhney do. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne likhwaayaa ye Muhammad Rasulullah ki taraf se suleh naamaa ki dastaawez hai. Suhel ne kaha agar hamein ye malum hota ke aap Rasulullah hain to na ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Kaba se roktey aur na aap se jang kartey. aap to sirf itna likhiye ke ''Muhammad-bin-Abdullaah'' is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Allah gawah hai ke main uska sachcha rasool hun chahe tum mujhe jhutlaatey raho. likho ji ''Muhammad-bin-Abdullaah'' Zohri ne bayan kya ke ye sab kuchh (narmii aur riaayat) sirf Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us irshad ka nateeja tha (jo pahley Budail (Raziallahu anhu) se keh chukey they) ke Quraish mujh se jo bhi aisa mutalba karengey jis se Allah Taala ki hurmaton ki ta'zeem maqsud hogi to main unke mutaalbey ko zaroor maan loonga, isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Suhel se farmaya lekin suleh ke liye pehli shart ye hogi ke tum log hamein Baitullah ke tawaaf karne ke liye janey doge. Suhel ne kaha qism Allah ki ham (is saal) aisa nahi honey dengey warna Arab kahengey ham maghloob ho gaey they (is liye ham ne ijazat de di) aainda saal ke liye ijazat hai. chunanche ye bhi likh liya. phir Suhel ne likha ke ye shart bhi (likh liijiye) ke hamari taraf ka jo shakhs bhi aap ke yahan jaeyga chahe wo aap ke Deen hi par kyon na ho aap usey hamein wapas kar dengey. musalmanon ne (ye shart sun kar kaha) sub'haan-Allaah! (eik shakhs ko) mushrikon ke hawale kis tarah kya ja sakta hai jo musalman ho kar aaya ho. abhi yahi baatein ho rahi thin ke abu-Jandal bin Suhail-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) apni bediyon ko ghaseet'tey huey aa pahunchey, wo Makka ke nashebii ilaaqey ki taraf se bhaagey they aur ab khud ko musalmanon ke samney daal diya tha. Suhel ne kaha aey Muhammad! ye pahlaa shakhs hai jiske liye (suleh naamaa ke mutaabiq) main mutalba karta hun ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein usey wapas kar dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke abhi to ham ne (suleh naame ki is baat ko) suleh naamaa mein likha bhi nahi hai (is liye jab suleh naamaa tay pa jaeyga uske baad isko laagu hona chaahiye) Suhel kehney laga ke Allah ki qism phir main kisi buniyad par bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suleh nahi karunga. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya achchha mujh par us aik ko de kar ehsan kar do. usne kaha ke main is silsiley mein ehsan bhi nahi kar sakta. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi hamein ehsan kar dena chahiye lekin us ne yahi jawab diya ke main aisa kabhi nahi kar sakta. albatta makooz ne kaha ke chaliye ham iska Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par ehsan kartey hain magar (uski baat nahi chalii) abu-Jandal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha muslmaanon! main musalman ho kar aaya hun. kya mujhey mushrikon ke hath mein de diya jaaeyga? kya mere sath jo aziyatein pahunchai gain thin. rawi ne bayan kya ke Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha aakhir main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya, kya ye waqia aur haqiqat nahi ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke Nabi hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kyon nahi ! maine arz kya, kya ham haq par nahi hain aur kya hamarey dushman baatil par nahi hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kyon nahi ! maine kaha phir apne Deen ke mamley mein kyon dabein . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya main Allah ka rasool hon, uske hukm ki nafarmani nahi kar sakta aur wahi mera madadgaar hai. maine kaha kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ham se ye nahi farmatey they ke ham Baitullah jaeinge aur uska tawaaf karengey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke theek hai lekin kya maine tum se ye kaha tha ke isi saal ham Baitullah pahunch jaengey. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine kaha nahi (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us qaid ke sath nahi farmaya tha) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir usmein koi shuba nahi ke tum Baitullah tak zaroor pahuncho gey aur aik din iska tawaaf karogey. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaya aur unse bhi yahi puchha ke abu-Bakar! kya ye haqiqat nahi ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke Nabi hain? unhon-ne bhi kaha ke kyon nahi. maine puchha kya ham haq par nahi hain? aur kya hamarey dushman baatil par nahi hain? unhon-ne kaha kyon nahin! maine kaha ke phir apne Deen ko kyon zaleel karein? Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : janaab! bila shak w shuba wo Allah ke rasool hain, aur apne rab ke hukm ki nafarmani nahi kar saktey aur rab hi unka madadgaar hai. to unki rassii mazbootii se pakad lo, Allah gawah hai ke wo haq par hain. maine kaha kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ham se ye nahi kehtey they ke an-qareeb ham Baitullah pahunchengey aur iska tawaaf karengey unhon-ne farmaya ke ye bhi sahi hai lekin kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aap se ye farmaya tha ke usi saal aap Baitullah pahunch jaengey. maine kaha ke nahi. phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha phir usmein bhi koi shak w shuba nahi ke aap aik na aik din Baitullah pahunchengey aur uska tawaaf karengey. Zohri ne bayan kya ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya baad mein maine apni jald bazi ki bharpaaii ke liye nek aamaal kiye. phir jab suleh naame se aap farigh ho chukey to sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke ab utho aur (jin janwaron ko sath laey ho unkii) qurbani kar lo aur sar bhi mundwaa lo. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Allah gawah hai sahaba mein se aik shakhs bhi na utha aur teen martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye jumla farmaya. jab koi na utha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Umme-Salma ke kheme mein gaey aur unse logon ke tarze-amal ka zikr kya. Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha aey Allah ke nabii! kya aap ye pasand karengey ke bahar tashrif ley jayen aur kisi se kuchh na kahin balke apna qurbani ka janwar zabah kar lein aur apne hajjaam ko bula lein jo aap ke baal moond de. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey. kisi se kuchh nahi kaha aur sab kuchh kya, apne janwar ki qurbani kar li aur apne hajjaam ko bulwaya jisne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baal moondey. jab sahaba ne dekha to wo bhi aik doosrey ke baal moondney lagey, aisa malum hota tha ke ranj w gham mein aik doosrey se lad padeingey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas (Makka se) chand momin auratein aaein to Allah Taala ne ye hukm nazil farmaya (ya أيها الذين آمنوا إذا جاءكم المؤمنات مهاجرات فامتحنوهن‏ (aey logo! jo eman la chukey ho jab tumharey paas momin auratein hijrat karke aaein to unka imtihaan ley ( بعصم الكوافر‏ ( tak. us din umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni 2 beeviyon ko talaaq di jo ab tak musalman na hui thin. unmein se aik ne to Muaawiya-bin-Abii-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anhu) se nikah kar liya tha aur dusri se Safwaan-bin-Umayya ne. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina wapas tashrif laey to Quraish ke aik fard Abu-Baseer (Raziallahu anhu) (Makka se faraar ho kar) hazir huey. wo musalman ho chukey they. Quraish ne unhein wapas leney ke liye 2 aadmiyon ko bheja aur unhon-ne aa kar kaha ke hamarey sath aap ka muaahida ho chuka hai. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abu-Baseer (Raziallahu anhu) ko wapas kar diya. Quraish ke donon afraad jab unhein wapas lekar lautey aur zul-Hulaifa pahunchey to khajoor khaney ke liye utrey jo unke sath thi. Abu-Baseer (Raziallahu anhu) ne unmein se aik se farmaya qism Allah ki tumhari talwaar bahut achi malum hoti hai. doosrey sathi ne talwaar niyaam se nikal di. us shakhs ne kaha haan Allah ki qism bahut hi zyada umda talwaar hai, main iska bahut baar tajriba kar chuka hun. Abu-Baseer (Raziallahu anhu) is par boley ke zara mujhey bhi to dikhao aur is tarah apne qabze mein kar liya phir us shakhs ne talwaar ke Malik ko aisi zarb lagai ke wo wahin thanda ho gaya. uska doosra sathi bhag kar Madina aaya aur masjid mein daudta hua dakhil hua Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab usey dekha to farmaya ye shakhs kuchh khof-zada malum hota hai. jab wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb pahuncha to kehney laga Allah ki qism mera sathi to maara gaya aur main bhi maara jaaunga (agar aap logon ne Abu-Baseer ko na rokaa) itney mein Abu-Baseer bhi aagey aur arz kya aey Allah ke Nabi ! Allah ki qism Allah Taala ne aap ki zimme-dari poori kar di, aap mujhey unke hawale kar chukey they lekin Allah Taala ne mujhey unse nijat dilaaii. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (teri maa ki kharaabii) agar iska koi aik bhi madadgaar hota to phir ladai ke sholey bhadak uthtey. jab unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ye alfaz suney to samajh gaey ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) phir kuffaar ke hawale kar dengey isliye wahan se nikal gaey aur samandar ke kinarey par aa gaey. rawi ne bayan kya ke apne ghar walon (Makka se) chhoot kar abu-jandal-bin-Suhail (Raziallahu anhu) bhi Abu-Baseer (Raziallahu anhu) se ja miley aur ab ye haal tha ke Quraish ka jo shakhs bhi Islam laataa (bajaaey Madina aaney ke) Abu-Baseer (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan (saahile-samandar par) chala jata. is tarah se aik jamat bin gaee aur Allah gawah hai ye log Quraish ke jis qafley ke mutaalliq bhi sun letey ke wo Sham (Syria) ja raha hai to usey rastey hi mein rok kar loot letey aur qaafila walon ko qatl kar detey. ab Quraish ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan Allah aur raham ka waasta de kar darkhaast bheji ke aap kisi ko bhejiin (Abu-Baseer (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke doosrey sathiyon ke yahan ke wo Quraish ko takleefein dene se ruk jaaein) aur uske baad jo shakhs bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan jaeyga (Makka se) usey amn hai. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke yahan apna aadmi bheja aur Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaaii وهو الذي كف أيديهم عنكم وأيديكم عنهم ببطن مكة من بعد أن أظفركم عليهم‏''aur wo zaat parwardigar jisne rok diya tha tumharey hathon ko unse aur unke hathon ko tum se (yani jang nahi ho saki thi) wadi Makka mein (Hudaibiya mein) baad mein iske ke tum ko ghalib kar diya tha un par yahan tak ke baat jahiliyat ke daur ki be-jaa himaayat tak pahunch gaee thii).'' unki hamiiyat ( jahiliyat ( ye thi ke unhon-ne (muaahidey mein bhi) aap ke liye Allah ke Nabi honey ka iqrar nahi kya isi tarah unhon-ne ( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم ( nahi likhney diya aur aap Baitullah janey se rukey rahey."
2733,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aurton ka (jo Makka se musalman honey ki wjah se hijrat karke Madina aati thiin) imtihaan letey they (Zohri ne) bayan kya ke ham tak ye riwayat pahunchi hai ke jab Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmai ke musalman wo sab kuchh un mushrikon ko wapas kar dein jo unhon-ne apni un beeviyon par kharch kya ho jo (ab musalman ho kar) hijrat kar aai hain aur musalmanon ko hukm diya ke kaafir aurton ko apne nikah mein na rakhein to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni 2 beeviyon Quraiba-bint-abii-Umayya aur aik jarwal Khuzai ki ladki ko talaaq de di. baad mein Quraiba se Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne shadi kar li thi (kyonke us waqt Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) musalman nahi huey they) aur dusri biwi se abu-Jaheem ne shadi kar li thi lekin jab kuffaar ne musalmanon ke un kharchon ko ada karne se inkar kya jo unhon-ne apni ( kaafira ( beeviyon par kiye they, to Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmai ( وإن فاتكم شىء من أزواجكم إلى الكفار فعاقبتم‏ ( ''aur tumhari beeviyon mein se koi kaafiron ke yahan chali gaee to wo muaawaza tum khud hi ley lo.'' ye wo muaawza tha jo musalman kuffaar mein se us shakhs ko detey jiski biwi hijrat karke (muslmaan honey ke baad kisi musalman ke nikah mein aa gaee ho ( to Allah ne ab ye hukm diya ke jis musalman ki biwi murtad ho kar (kuffaar ke yahaan) chali jaey uske (mahar w nafqa ke) kharchey un kuffaar ki aurton ke mehar se ada kar diye jayen jo hijrat karke aa gaee hain (aur kisi musalman ne unse nikah kar liya hai) bhale hi hamarey paas iska koi saboot nahi ke koi muhaajira bhi eman ke baad murtad hui hon aur hamein ye riwayat bhi malum hui ke Abu-Baseer-bin-Usaid Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein momin w muhajir ki haisiyat se muaahide ki muddat ke andar hi hazir huey to akhnas-bin-Shuraiq ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik tahreer likhi jis mein us ne (Abu-Baseer (Raziallahu anhu) ki waapsii ka ( mutalba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya tha. phir unhon-ne hadis poori bayan ki."
2734,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ka zikr kya jinhoney Bani-Israeel ke kisi doosrey shakhs se aik hazaar ashrafii qarz maanga aur us ne aik muqarrara muddat tak ke liye de diya.
2735,"Barira (Raziallahu anhu) apne makaatibat ke silsiley mein unse madad maangney aaein to unhon-ne kaha ke agar tum chaho to tumharey maalikon ko) poori qeemat ( de dun aur tumhari 'walaa' mere hogi. phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maine iska zikr kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya unhein to khareed ley aur aazad kar de. 'walaa' to bahar-haal usi ki hogi jo aazad kar de. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par tashrif laey aur farmaya un logon ko kya ho gaya hai jo aisi shartein lagaatey hain jinka koi pata (daleel, sanad) kitabullah mein nahi hai, jisne bhi koi aisi shart lagai jiska pata (daleel, sanad) kitabullah mein na ho to chahe aisi so shartein laga ley unse kuchh fayda na uthaaeyga."
2736,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala ke ninyaanwe naam hain yani aik kam so. jo shakhs un sab ko mehfooz rakhega wo jannat mein dakhil hoga.''
2737,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko khaibar mein aik qat'aa zameen mili to aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein mashware ke liye hazir huey aur arz kya ya Rasulullah! mujhey khaibar mein aik zameen ka tukda mila hai us se behtar maal mujhey ab tak kabhi nahi mila tha, aap iske mutaalliq kya hukm farmatey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar ji chahey to asl zameen apne milkiyat mein baqi rakh aur paidawar sadqa kar de. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko us shart ke sath sadqa kar diya ke na usey bechaa jaeyga na iska hiba kya jaeyga aur na usmein wiraasat chalegii. usey aap ne mohtajon ke liye, rishtedaron ke liye aur ghulam aazad karaaney ke liye, Allah ke Deen ki tableegh aur ishaa'at ke liye aur mahmaanon ke liye sadqa ( waqf ( kar diya aur ye ke iska mutwallii agar dastoor ke mutabiq usmein se apni zarurat ke mutabiq wsool kar ley ya kisi mohtaaj ko de to is par koi ilzam nahi. ibne-Aun ne bayan kya ke jab maine us hadis ka zikr Ibne-Sirin se kya to unhon-ne farmaya ke) mutwallii ( usmein se maal jama karne ka irada na rakhta ho."
